          <li><strong><a href="/how-to-do-geo/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">How to Do GEO</a></strong> — the tactical execution guide: eight hands-on steps with practical actions and tools. Use this alongside the roadmap for task-level guidance within each phase.</li>
          <li><strong><a href="/geo-strategy/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">GEO Strategy</a></strong> — the decision layer covering when to invest, how to prioritise, and agency vs DIY. Read this before committing to the roadmap if you are still evaluating whether to proceed.</li>
